oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gray and Dudley Grand Opening
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Advertising; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and gray on white) announcing the grand opening of Gray and Dudley, a new restaurant at the 21c Museum Hotel, a multi-venue contemporary art museum, boutique hotel and restaurant, in Nashville. Poster features woodcuts of birds.
